title: 2012, 2013 & 2014 Chevy Camaro ZL1 6.2L Air Intake Installation
description:
See how easy it is to add more performance to the 2012 and 2013 Chevy Camaro ZL1 6.2L.

K&N 63-3079 air intake modification showed an estimated gain of 31.7 horsepower at 4300 RPM when tested on the K&N dynamometer.

K&N 63-3079 fits the following: 
2014 CHEVROLET CAMARO ZL1 6.2L V8 
2013 CHEVROLET CAMARO ZL1 6.2L V8
2012 CHEVROLET CAMARO ZL1 6.2L V8
tags: K&N Air Intake System, Chevy Camaro ZL1, 2012,2013,2014, how to install, cold air intake
